data.title: Copies - A Proclamation by The Governor, Kirk Fordice, 1996
data.text:
From the Collection:

This collection includes correspondence, photographs, and memorabilia including small and large framed artwork from Nunnelee's legislative and congressional years, news clippings primarily spanning 2011-2015, and Mississippi State University-related clothing and memorabilia. Books from the collection are located in the CPRC's reading room.
